{"tid":1559642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"收到風美國議員睇香港民意決定推唔推人權法上到參議院/眾議院。","createTime":"2019-09-11T02:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T16:24:53.000Z","uid":62011,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"289b4f51e83a430f87a1e00f9178cde3cf75c008","tid":1559642,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:00:12.000Z","msg":"從今日開始，每人每日係twitter最少Send 五個外國議員，直至人權法通過。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dLreGS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dLreGS</a><br />\n<br />\n=====【目標】=====<br />\n－向美國參眾兩院請願，加速通過《香港人權及民主法案》2019，令美國可向中共及香港施壓，監督香港確立雙普選，達到自治。<br />\n－對象：參眾兩院議員<br />\n<br />\n=====【主要訊息】=====<br />\n1.) 香港人支持法案通過。(PLEASE PASS Hong Kong Human Right and Democracy Act) <br />\n2.) 香港人要求雙普選。(We want dual sufferage to select our legislators(senator) and Chief Executive of HK)<br />\n3.) 如無法達至民主化，港人明白和已準備接受全面制裁。<br />\n(Please impose sanction on HK if necessary for Democracy)<br />\n3.) 中共港共破壞香港自治，而且向市民施暴，情況危急。<br />\n(The CCP is destroying HK autonomy and violating HK people with violence.<br />\n4.) 香港人乃反共先鋒，值得世界支持。<br />\n(HK people are willing to counter against the CCP. <br />\n<br />\n=====【注意事項】=====<br />\n1.) 此法案乃兩黨合作(bipartisan)進行，切切避免將兩黨之爭拉入香港議題，不要和特朗普總統，共和黨或民主黨割席。<br />\n2.) 如見到有人罵Trump或有人罵民主黨，不要捲入罵戰，繼續跟他們說【主要訊息】就行。<br />\n3.) 記住你的目標是參眾兩院，這次是兩黨都想搶功勞。群眾罵Trump，會令民主黨更高興地推法案，反之亦然，毋須介懷。<br />\n4.) 關鍵時刻，我們可能會發動高密度的Tweet戰。屆時不要怕spam，你佔機場都不怕騷擾人，你tag人怕騷擾人嗎？<br />\n<br />\n=====【工具】=====<br />\n1.) 民主黨參議員twitter生成器<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2k4kN9G\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2k4kN9G&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRetOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=c8dcbdb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2k4kN9G</a><br />\n2.) 共和黨參議員twitter生成器<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2kBszrN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kBszrN&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRetOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=6b0acb04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2kBszrN</a><br />\n3.) 民主黨眾議員twitter生成器<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2lKzDT7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lKzDT7&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRetOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=69f07cb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2lKzDT7</a><br />\n4.) 共和黨眾議員twitter生成器<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2kyIJCp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kyIJCp&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRetOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=284bec54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2kyIJCp</a><br />\n5.) 參議員列表<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/cspan/lists/senators\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcspan%2Flists%2Fsenators&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRetOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=69324e60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/cspan/lists/senators</a><br />\n6.) 眾議員列表<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/cspan/lists/u-s-representatives/members\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcspan%2Flists%2Fu-s-representatives%2Fmembers&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRetOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=3077752b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/cspan/lists/u-s-representatives/members</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家要繼續推推阿，唔係進入國會議程就算，你唔做野人地就會以為你根本就唔係爭取民主。"},{"pid":"3c8e68a4cdb2ab4f44e86af75f686f624bb0b41a","tid":1559642,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZd64DE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZd64DE.jpg&h=33235d4d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tFcr4DF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtFcr4DF.jpg&h=4f032819&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08398c42ab914cc341fd866b03488aa7a1bdb88d","tid":1559642,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:01:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d725982a5ba20a7e611f3b31c2db86339fc1ff68","tid":1559642,